CC Dumas presents: SHAAM SHAANDAAR
Not a sequel. Not a scene.
Just one blockbuster evening you can’t miss!

On 31st May, from 4 PM onwards, step into a world where Bollywood dreams come alive!
Get ready to dress up as your favourite Bollywood character, sip on Bunty soda, snack on chaat, kulfi & gola, and shop your heart out at curated stalls filled with filmy finds.

Expect music, filmy flashbulbs, Insta-worthy corners, and a whole lot of masti.

Entry by registration only – DM us now to grab your spot!
Because when the vibe is filmy…
Party toh banti hai, boss!

They’re loud, legendary, and larger-than-life — just like our vibe.
The characters are out, the clues are set, and the drama has officially begun.
From the timeless romantics to the total rebels — they’ve all made it to Shaam Shaandar.

But hold up…
Picture abhi baaki hai mere dost.

This is just the interval.
The plot thickens, the twist is coming, and YOU are part of the next act.
Stay tuned — ‘cause this filmy shaam is only getting started.

#ShaamShaandar #FilmyFeelsOnly #BollywoodCharacters #drop3 #PictureAbhiBaakiHai #ComingSoon

Shaam Shaandar begins… with a feeling. A scene. A memory.
Before the lights, before the music — it’s the characters who take the spotlight.✨

Not the stars, but the unforgettable roles that shaped our screens (and hearts).🫶🏻🌟

We let the drama unfold… one iconic look at a time.
From the hopeless romantic to the fearless fighter — each one drops a clue.👀

Which character do you connect with the most — and why?
Drop it in the comments. Your answer might just say more than you think.🤔 

This is just the beginning.
The story of Shaam Shaandar is about to unfold — thoda filmy, thoda classy, and a whole lotta drama.

#ShaamShaandar #FilmyFeelsOnly #Drop2 #GuessThePlot #ComingSoon

At CC Dumas, we’re welcoming the week the best way we know how — with chilled summer drinks, good food, and a space that feels like a mini escape. 

Whether you’re catching up with a friend or treating yourself to a solo coffee moment, there’s always a table waiting for you.

Ready for a refreshing start?
